Package: libpqxx-7.9
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libpq5
Description: C++ library for PostgreSQL 7.9.x
 libpqxx is a C++ library for accessing PostgreSQL databases.
 It provides a set of classes and functions to make working with
 PostgreSQL easier and more intuitive from C++ code.
 .
 This package contains the shared library for libpqxx 7.9.x.

Package: libpqxx-7.9-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libpqxx-7.9 (= ${binary:Version}), libpq-dev, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Development files for libpqxx 7.9.x
 This package contains the headers and development files needed to build
 applications using libpqxx 7.9.x.

